lead_paragraph: A bargaining team for the Chicago teachers' union will decide on Monday whether to accept a contract offer from the financially troubled district, averting a potential strike and preventing a new embarrassment for Mayor Rahm Emanuel.

headline.main: Chicago Teachers Bargaining Team to Decide on Contract Offer
